{"tid":130037,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"駿傑集團首掛　下午突遭證監勒令停牌","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:21:41.000Z","uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89d16e01fc13e298df2090378a913d1614729b54","tid":130037,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170222/bkn-20170222130909418-0222_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170222%2Fbkn-20170222130909418-0222_00842_001.html&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7HadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9540468b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170222/bkn-20170222130909418-0222_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今早以配售方式掛牌的駿傑集團控股(08188)下午開市後突停牌，通告指，是依據上市條例第8(1)條，應證券及期貨事務監察委員會之指令。<br />\n<br />\n對於駿傑上市半日遭證監會勒令停牌，證監會發言人表示對個別事件不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，今年先後有3隻全配售創板股被叫停上市計劃，早前成功闖關的火鍋店「小肥牛」母企國茂則要將承配人數目大幅增加至211人。<br />\n<br />\n駿傑今早順利上市，而其首25名承配人僅獲配61.12%股份，是今年大戶比例最為分散的創板新股。<br />\n<br />\n在早間上市儀式期間，問及主席莊峻岳是否有特別策略令公司上市成功過關，他表示，作為股東不太清楚分銷的詳情，但指選用知名包銷商有助順利上市。至於會否擔心股價波動而引來監管當局調查，他表示影響股價的因素很多，不能一概而論；又表示，是次集資額雖只有4千多萬元，但已足夠公司1至2年發展用途。<br />\n<br />\n駿傑集團控股今早開市價3.46港元，較配售價0.54元飆5.4倍，高位見3.51元，高配售價5.5倍，半日收報3.47元，高配售價5.42倍，成交金額6,947萬元。如不計手續費，以半日收市價3.47元計，每手帳賺11,720元。"},{"pid":"902385bf36989e01a210293617de9d1c89c0407a","tid":130037,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6184649d4da22896af4c255010eb334ef87be092","tid":130037,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"仲夠膽上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed360512a1a6e2753853aac12ea18f5d625919a9","tid":130037,"uid":71138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:47:14.000Z","msg":"聽日復牌"},{"pid":"88fa6a930d49b4b1fa81b07d2324f33700896722","tid":130037,"uid":33272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"沽壓好大"},{"pid":"88130fe451a0f94688175233fc45509337b559a7","tid":130037,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲夠膽上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人有多大膽,地有多大產"},{"pid":"9db4bb20d22dd5ee29686bda0ddb850252b5f923","tid":130037,"uid":88995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55eb7efe201b2ca6cdab3fd724f015e43fb1c55b","tid":130037,"uid":71138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:17:39.000Z","msg":"跌八成"},{"pid":"3b8833a03b122e4e633415736d3c8a723bc4bde4","tid":130037,"uid":43473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升番"}]}